# Comprehensive Technical Comparison: Claude Code/MCP vs OpenCode Integration Protocols

## Table of Contents

1. [Protocol Architecture Overview](#1-protocol-architecture-overview)
2. [Tool Definitions: MCP vs Bun Tool](#2-tool-definitions-mcp-vs-bun-tool)
3. [Command Documentation: Slash Command vs Command Doc](#3-command-documentation-slash-command-vs-command-doc)
