| `SessionStart` | `"startup"` (keyword) | `node "${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/scripts/session-lifecycle-hook.mjs" SessionStart` | 10s | When Claude Code session starts |
| `SessionEnd` | *(none, matches all)* | `node "${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/scripts/session-lifecycle-hook.mjs" SessionEnd` | 10s | When session ends |
| `Stop` | *(none, matches all)* | `node "${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/scripts/stop-review-gate-hook.mjs"` | 60s | When user stops Claude Code |
| `PostToolUse` | `"^.*trae:review.*$"` (regex) | `node "${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/scripts/session-lifecycle-hook.mjs" PostReview` | 5s | After `trae:review` slash command is used |

**Matcher Semantics:**
- **`"startup"`** -- a special keyword that means "match all session start events"
- **Regex string** (e.g., `"^.*trae:review.*$"`) -- matches against the tool/command name
- **Absent** -- matches all events of that hook type

